{
  "page": "Wolf Pack",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>Wolf Pack</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Sellsword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sellsword\">sellsword</a> company operating in <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wolf_Pack&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Wolf Pack was founded by <a href=\"/index.php/Hallis_Hornwood\" title=\"Hallis Hornwood\">Hallis Hornwood</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Timotty_Snow\" title=\"Timotty Snow\">Timotty Snow</a> in the aftermath of the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a> and the collapse of the <a href=\"/index.php/Triarchy\" title=\"Triarchy\">Triarchy</a>, when the <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myr</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyrosh</a> were hiring sellswords in anticipation of the <a href=\"/index.php/Daughters%27_War\" title=\"Daughters&#39; War\">Daughters' War</a>. At the time, the new free company consisted only of <a href=\"/index.php/Northmen\" title=\"Northmen\">northmen</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> who are often dubbed \"<a href=\"/index.php/Wolf\" title=\"Wolf\">wolves</a>\" on account of the <a href=\"/index.php/Direwolf\" title=\"Direwolf\">direwolf</a> sigil of the rulers of the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wolf_Pack&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - The Hooded Hand.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template:Sellsword_companies\" title=\"Template:Sellsword companies\"><span title=\"View this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">v</span></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/index.php/Template_talk:Sellsword_companies\" title=\"Template talk:Sellsword companies\"><span title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";;background:none transparent;border:none;\">d</span